Cell["\<\
We can extract the expansion coefficient data for the L=3 solutions along the \
sequence.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9203845041048517`*^9, 3.9203846406669273`*^9}, {
  3.9203846795918407`*^9, 3.920384718306408*^9}, {3.920384755583188*^9, 
